Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,社群网站遇见了高傲人妻，  因丈夫太冷漠而欲求不满\N{\fs14\fnKaiTi}希島あいり【MEYD-499】{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道在旁人看来我们是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,普通的情侣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是母子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我付钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,平常都让你付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想付啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,约会的钱都是我出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡厅和电影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,宾馆也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是妈妈活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个普通的主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,过着无趣的每天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,丈夫是认真工作的上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何不良嗜好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家虽然都很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得他是不是根本不需我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得有小孩之后会不会有些改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,丈夫老说还太早了一直推脱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他还很寡欲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,三个月都不一定有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我很欲求不满
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,从损友那里听到了妈妈活这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和年轻男生约会，给他零用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我一开始也觉得没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,试了之后总觉得母性本能大爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,会想帮他做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且年轻男生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那个超猛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,做爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可以做好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,丈夫都不能满足我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,果然会做那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也只有那个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你找对象的APP吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,交友APP是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是配对APP啦，传给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让女的请客也太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当打发时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看看有什么样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都是大学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,都是帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉都好轻浮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和其他人不一样，被他不做作的资料给吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次约会我很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不付钱的话，对方会不会不理我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,担心会不会被当作孤独剩女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫做宏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫爱里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,参加这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮，吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么像你这样的人会上那种网站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，不该问的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我结婚以来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但很无聊，想有一点变化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想像以前一样心动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,恋爱的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都一把年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得还蛮不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,宏君你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前就很喜欢年长女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,温柔而且沉稳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,又有包容力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,同班的人都说喜欢年轻女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我却喜欢班导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,宏君他在大学上课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为了优先课业他没在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想支援他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我来付吧，就是为此来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下来要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我给了他零用钱请，他跟我做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他会贪求我数次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,上次感觉到自己是个女人已经是好几年前了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像要真的喜欢上爱里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不会说要你和丈夫分手这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是从今往后也请和我见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经没办法回头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,话说，之前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我去朋友住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是个超不妙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哥，你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你，为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我打工刚结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,刚结束．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你和这么漂亮的人在约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么约会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是他妹妹，叫春实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,交往多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱坐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别吵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,脸超漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很不会化妆，可以教我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,下次来我家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,先来交换联络方式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太没礼貌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,手机拿出来一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哥你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是我的email
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这边是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明天来家里吗？妹妹一直说好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去你家里没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明天正好休息，要一起出门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，明天约好要和朋友喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,家人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等好久了，欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,春实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来教我化妆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我平常在女仆咖啡工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,女仆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,和你很合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爱里小姐也要穿穿看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对很合的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没那种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这种比较煽情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这也很合身的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不适合啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没那种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会很适合的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哥，你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哥你干嘛，时间停止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这件我借你吧，打工的日寸候再还就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那慢来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别弄脏床哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一把年纪了．．．好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我妹有点蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱的妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着这个看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,摆一些姿势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,摆摆看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再...再多一些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,手抓一下上面的头饰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说说看，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,主...主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,独处的时候再做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,说，请温柔一点主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不然叫叫看，  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害羞，再说一遍看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌，等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不好’巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看不见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再开一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都说妹妹在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再脱一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我流很多汗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹妹．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还要脱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,舔舔看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,其实以前有穿过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛这样看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你一直摸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,别闻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那眼睛闭起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可以撑开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,脚张开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.57,0:24:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是流出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.38,0:24:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你清干净吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,床会脏的啦，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.52,0:24:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.30,0:24:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,被人发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.47,0:24:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤月兑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.65,0:24:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.89,0:24:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.06,0:25:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,面向这边
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.00,0:25:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.46,0:25:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.37,0:25:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.09,0:26:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.25,0:26:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.25,0:27:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再多摸一些
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.12,0:27:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,会被发现的  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.00,0:27:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,用女仆的方式说话看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.42,0:27:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.36,0:27:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.56,0:27:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,说让您舒服之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.49,0:27:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,请用爱里的嘴舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.27,0:27:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.10,0:27:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.70,0:28:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样看我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.64,0:28:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.58,0:28:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.82,0:28:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.16,0:28:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,说说看，您舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.60,0:29:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一边舔一边说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.10,0:29:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.41,0:29:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.81,0:29:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.38,0:29:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多说一些
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.73,0:30:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.97,0:30:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.09,0:30:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.13,0:30:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.60,0:30:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.27,0:30:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.48,0:30:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可能忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.76,0:31:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.69,0:31:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在这吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.10,0:31:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.03,0:31:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,主人，不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.44,0:31:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.54,0:31:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.64,0:31:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.04,0:31:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说还不能射出来，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.55,0:31:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.85,0:31:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的小穴里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.50,0:31:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.64,0:31:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请在爱里的小穴射出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.65,0:32:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.48,0:32:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.09,0:32:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.26,0:32:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,躺好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.56,0:32:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.00,0:33:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.31,0:33:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.52,0:33:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.58,0:34:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.54,0:35:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.52,0:36:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.65,0:36:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,换个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.09,0:36:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.84,0:37:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那样舔得话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.71,0:38:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.28,0:38:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,陕不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.98,0:38:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.25,0:39:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.09,0:39:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.64,0:39:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我去吧主人，说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.98,0:39:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.38,0:39:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.32,0:39:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.39,0:40:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.13,0:40:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的，擦一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.08,0:40:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.94,0:41:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.44,0:41:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,里面可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.01,0:41:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请射在里面主人，说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.35,0:41:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请射好多在我的里面
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.40,0:41:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.17,0:41:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.84,0:42:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.87,0:43:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.65,0:43:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说谢谢主人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.89,0:43:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.93,0:43:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.43,0:44:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.84,0:44:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.77,0:44:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.11,0:44:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.25,0:44:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋包饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.92,0:44:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.12,0:44:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗，偶尔这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.42,0:44:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.89,0:45:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不会，只是觉得好像是小孩吃的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.13,0:45:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗，帮你加番茄酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.82,0:45:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这啥
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.29,0:45:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.43,0:45:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你注入爱情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.26,0:45:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.78,0:46:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,久违的吃蛋包饭还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.30,0:46:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.60,0:46:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.17,0:46:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.21,0:46:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.98,0:46:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.59,0:46:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不用害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.66,0:46:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.43,0:46:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好好奉侍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.70,0:47:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.42,0:47:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还在害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.99,0:47:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.57,0:48:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要请你好好服侍我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.08,0:48:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.66,0:48:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.93,0:48:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,舔的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.17,0:48:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,主人舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.58,0:48:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那里好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.23,0:49:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.99,0:49:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.66,0:49:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.44,0:49:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.70,0:50:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说，请多摸摸我下流的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.15,0:50:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请多摸摸我下流的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.46,0:51:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,太赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.54,0:51:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.89,0:51:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.93,0:51:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.54,0:51:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,主人请看
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.38,0:52:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,果然硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.13,0:52:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,勒得好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.94,0:52:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我看清楚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.58,0:52:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.15,0:52:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要藏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.72,0:52:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.39,0:52:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.96,0:52:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.79,0:52:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.46,0:52:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.60,0:53:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,自己撑开来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.88,0:53:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.82,0:53:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.26,0:53:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.13,0:53:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想被舔要怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.80,0:53:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,主人请舔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.41,0:53:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,自己过来贴住我的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.49,0:54:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.15,0:55:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.19,0:55:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.64,0:55:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好美味
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.41,0:55:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.98,0:56:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.06,0:56:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,主人的肉棒好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.86,0:56:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,主人的肉棒变硬的话要怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.04,0:56:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.79,0:56:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.19,0:56:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.89,0:57:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,变大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.20,0:57:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,用嘴来服侍看
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.47,0:57:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,用嘴．．
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.43,0:57:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.77,0:58:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.38,0:58:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请变得更舒服，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.68,0:58:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.18,0:58:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再深一些
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.86,0:59:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋那边也．，，
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.92,0:59:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.80,0:59:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.52,0:59:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要问一下我哪边舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.65,1:00:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那边舒服呢，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.06,1:00:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,内侧的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.26,1:00:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.46,1:00:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对，那边好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.31,1:00:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说一些煽情的话吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.85,1:00:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬呢，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.89,1:00:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.03,1:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这么硬，舒服吗主人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.27,1:00:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.04,1:00:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.97,1:00:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,陕忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.54,1:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也．．．
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.09,1:01:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,也舔我的蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.16,1:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好美味
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.03,1:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.61,1:01:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小穴怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.92,1:01:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.49,1:01:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.52,1:01:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那．．
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.30,1:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想被插入吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.00,1:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,请插入我湿答答的小穴里
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.45,1:02:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那自己插入
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.99,1:02:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,自己放进来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.49,1:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.70,1:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,主人插进来的样子
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.47,1:02:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请好好看清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.13,1:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,插进来—I
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.14,1:03:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,主人的肉棒很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.38,1:03:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,主人的肉棒插的好深
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.92,1:03:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.27,1:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.48,1:04:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.32,1:04:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很下流呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.26,1:04:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.19,1:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.95,1:04:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.25,1:05:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.65,1:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.05,1:06:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,主人好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.47,1:06:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.72,1:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.10,1:06:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.14,1:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠过来一点
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.72,1:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要从后面插入了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.42,1:07:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,主人的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.83,1:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面来很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.70,1:07:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面插...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.52,1:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.01,1:08:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看的一清二楚哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.31,1:08:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下流的地方被主人看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.53,1:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.98,1:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.42,1:08:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,主人里面好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.07,1:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.91,1:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样用手
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.45,1:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请用力的插我，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.30,1:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.34,1:09:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看脸
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.65,1:09:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.09,1:10:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.99,1:10:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.97,1:10:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.28,1:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.15,1:11:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那自己撑开来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.02,1:11:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.59,1:11:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我更多
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.68,1:11:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.66,1:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.33,1:11:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,主人，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.00,1:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.24,1:12:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.36,1:12:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.84,1:12:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也快射了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.18,1:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是您的下流女仆
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.95,1:12:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我射在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.19,1:13:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,请主人射在我的里面
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.51,1:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.42,1:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.35,1:13:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.54,1:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.48,1:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,夹得好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.15,1:13:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.08,1:13:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.02,1:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.12,1:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想要主人热热的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.79,1:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.99,1:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,多拜托我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.20,1:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,请射在里面主人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.17,1:14:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.84,1:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请射好多出来，巴
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.88,1:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.65,1:14:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.73,1:15:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.15,1:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后过了一段时间
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.45,1:15:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,宏君的大学开始了定期测试
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.69,1:15:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,约好了考试结束之前不见面的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.30,1:15:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哥的大学如果测验没过的话会被留级的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.00,1:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.77,1:15:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱，居然害羞了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.71,1:15:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别捉弄我啦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.01,1:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,爱里小姐如果在店里工作的话肯定会是头牌
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.25,1:16:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,来试试看
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.46,1:16:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样，萌萌啾
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.70,1:16:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.10,1:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.20,1:16:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对，然后
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.40,1:16:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,萌萌啾
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.74,1:16:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.05,1:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,萌萌啾
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.98,1:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.55,1:16:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,下次做给哥看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.59,1:16:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.60,1:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一个礼拜后
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.18,1:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系，我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.27,1:17:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,测验结束了，明天丈夫要出差，要不要来我家
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.24,1:17:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.65,1:17:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在此恭候，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.09,1:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.33,1:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.14,1:18:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.61,1:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,特别做给你的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.18,1:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,测验努力过的奖励
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.75,1:18:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今天一天我都是你的女仆
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.70,1:18:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为了主人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.64,1:18:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,做了充满爱情的蛋包饭哦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.61,1:18:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.38,1:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为了变得更好吃我要施魔法了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.76,1:19:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,变得美味吧，  变美味吧，  萌萌啾
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.34,1:19:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好美味
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.54,1:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.45,1:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,烫
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.49,1:19:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.32,1:19:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我来喂你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.25,1:19:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如何，好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.02,1:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.48,1:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.52,1:20:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.99,1:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮您洗身体哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.72,1:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.11,1:20:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多用舌头一些
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.45,1:21:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.30,1:22:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,下面也
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.68,1:22:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.35,1:22:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.52,1:22:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.29,1:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒也好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.63,1:23:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.85,1:23:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗，主人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.78,1:23:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.45,1:23:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.23,1:23:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？主人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.26,1:23:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.40,1:23:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,夹住了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.91,1:23:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.48,1:23:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,乳交
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.15,1:23:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.82,1:23:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部太小了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.49,1:23:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啦
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.32,1:23:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.36,1:23:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.83,1:24:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.43,1:24:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.81,1:24:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,前端也
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.38,1:24:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,变的比刚才还硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.43,1:24:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.10,1:24:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.14,1:24:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,舔吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.58,1:24:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.25,1:24:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.55,1:25:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那里好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.86,1:25:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.79,1:25:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.65,1:25:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.46,1:25:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.33,1:25:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.47,1:25:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,多用一些口水
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.24,1:26:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.11,1:26:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,变得更舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.15,1:26:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,主人有没有痒的地方
